-----
Command to run the servers:
go to the folder where your server is located then run the below command:
json-server server_name.json
Example: json-server db_Sau.json
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1zkgdLZEdwM
-------
Response validation by Json path and Jacson library is described in this project and Json handling.
Use of JASONpath-> This eats a lot of memory hence not recomended for boig or medium size responses.
Gson-> if response is not very big and complex then use this.
Jacson-> if the response is very complex use this.
